     mso-bidi-font-weight:bold">Mahalnya&nbsp; harga kebutuhan pokok&nbsp; yang harus di penuhi oleh RT nelayan, cenderung semakin memperbesar kemiskinan</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;
     mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold">.</span><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;
